<br>
Firing at the Earth would be pointless, the beam would be dispersed by the atmosphere.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://news.bbc.co.uk/olmedia/780000/images/_782696_laser150.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
